                  "fill": "#727272",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 460,
                  "content": "Born and raised in Palombara Sabina, a hilltop village outside Rome, Nonna Patrizia has been cooking these ancient pasta recipes her whole life. Now she shares them with the world.",
